name: SOLAPE
description: SOL-Ape is the Solana ecosystem’s favorite meme DEX, built for apes, by apes. Leveraging the power of the Openbook protocol, SolApe has a reputation for offering CLOB trading on a variety of SPL assets – and providing its users with a seamless interface for doing so. The $SOLAPE token offers utility via staking and yield protocols, as well as airdrop rewards for high-end holders. The apes continue to meme, experiment, and build upon the existing foundations of Solana's oldest trader community.
